text.tspan: Bringing in the good news we announce the gospel
Serving in the priesthood, reigning in the kingship.
We enjoy the double portion of the land;
Christ, the serving priest and ruling One within us.
Keeps us in the oneness, our eternal stand!
Exercise your spirit in the royal priesthood
And the resurrection power will engage;
By cooperating we are now securing
Out participating in the kingdom age.
